<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>{% block title %}腕表维修服务报告{% endblock %}</title>
    <style>
        @page { size: A4; margin: 15mm 12mm; }
        * { box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #1f2937;
            font-size: 13px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .report-header {
            border-bottom: 3px solid #2563eb;
            padding-bottom: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        .header-top { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start; }
        .brand {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #1e40af;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .brand-sub { color: #6b7280; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 4px; }
        .report-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #1f2937;
            margin: 20px 0 4px;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
        }
        .order-meta {
            text-align: center;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .info-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .info-card {
            background: #f8fafc;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 14px 16px;
        }
        .info-card h3 {
            margin: 0 0 10px;
            padding-bottom: 6px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #3b82f6;
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #1e3a8a;
        }
        .info-row {
            display: flex;
            padding: 4px 0;
            font-size: 12.5px;
        }
        .info-label {
            width: 90px;
            color: #6b7280;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .info-value { color: #111827; font-weight: 500; }

        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 12.5px;
        }
        table th {
            background: #eff6ff;
            color: #1e40af;
            padding: 10px 12px;
            text-align: left;
            font-weight: 600;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #bfdbfe;
        }
        table td {
            padding: 9px 12px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        table tr:nth-child(even) td { background: #fafafa; }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #1e3a8a;
            margin: 24px 0 12px;
            padding-left: 12px;
            border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;
        }
        .inspection-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .inspection-item {
            background: #f9fafb;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 10px 14px;
        }
        .inspection-item .label {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }
        .inspection-item .value {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #111827;
        }
        .inspection-item .unit { font-size: 11px; color: #6b7280; margin-left: 3px; }
        .inspection-item.alert {
            background: #fef2f2;
            border-color: #fecaca;
        }
        .inspection-item.alert .value { color: #dc2626; }

        .compare-images {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 12px;
            margin: 16px 0;
        }
        .compare-images img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 140px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 6px;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        .compare-images .caption {
            font-size: 11px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin-top: 4px;
        }

        .progress-timeline {
            margin: 16px 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .progress-timeline .item {
            display: flex;
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px dashed #e5e7eb;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        .progress-timeline .time {
            width: 130px;
            color: #6b7280;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .progress-timeline .action {
            width: 90px;
            color: #2563eb;
            font-weight: 600;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .progress-timeline .detail {
            flex: 1;
            color: #374151;
        }

        .pricing-card {
            background: #eff6ff;
            border: 1px solid #bfdbfe;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 16px 0;
        }
        .pricing-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 6px 0;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        .pricing-row.total {
            font-size: 17px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #1e3a8a;
            padding-top: 14px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            border-top: 2px dashed #93c5fd;
        }
        .pricing-row .amount { font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; }

        .warranty-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ecfdf5 0%, #d1fae5 100%);
            border: 1px solid #6ee7b7;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .warranty-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #059669;
            color: white;
            padding: 3px 10px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        .signatures {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 40px;
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding-top: 30px;
        }
        .signature-block {
            border-top: 1px solid #9ca3af;
            padding-top: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6b7280;
        }

        .footer-note {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 14px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 10.5px;
            color: #9ca3af;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="report-header">
        <div class="header-top">
            <div>
                <h1 class="brand">{{ studio_name }}</h1>
                <div class="brand-sub">
                    {{ studio_address }} | 服务电话：{{ studio_phone }} | 邮箱：{{ studio_email }}
                </div>
            </div>
            <div style="text-align:right;">
                <div style="font-size:11px;color:#6b7280;">报告生成</div>
                <div style="font-size:12.5px;font-weight:600;">{{ report.generatedAt }}</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="report-title">腕表维修服务报告</div>
        <div class="order-meta">
            工单号：{{ report.orderNumber }} | 生成日期：{{ report.generatedAt|date('Y-m-d') }}
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="info-grid">
        <div class="info-card">
            <h3>📋 客户信息</h3>
            <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">客户姓名</span><span class="info-value">{{ report.customer.name }}</span></div>
            <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">联系电话</span><span class="info-value">{{ report.customer.phone ?: '—' }}</span></div>
            <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">电子邮箱</span><span class="info-value">{{ report.customer.email ?: '—' }}</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card">
            <h3>⌚ 腕表信息</h3>
            <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">品牌 / 型号</span><span class="info-value">{{ report.watch.brand }} {{ report.watch.model }}</span></div>
            <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">表壳序列号</span><span class="info-value">{{ report.watch.caseSerial ?: '—' }}</span></div>
            <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">机芯号</span><span class="info-value">{{ report.watch.movementName ?: report.watch.movementCode }}</span></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-title">🔍 检测数据</div>
    {% if report.inspection %}
    <div class="inspection-grid">
        <div class="inspection-item">
            <div class="label">振频</div>
            <div class="value">{{ report.inspection.frequency ?: '—' }}<span class="unit">vph</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="inspection-item">
            <div class="label">摆幅</div>
            <div class="value">{{ report.inspection.amplitude ?: '—' }}<span class="unit">°</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="inspection-item">
            <div class="label">日差</div>
            <div class="value">{{ report.inspection.rate ?: '—' }}<span class="unit">s/d</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="inspection-item">
            <div class="label">位差</div>
            <div class="value">{{ report.inspection.beatError ?: '—' }}<span class="unit">ms</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="inspection-item">
            <div class="label">动力储存</div>
            <div class="value">{{ report.inspection.powerReserve ?: '—' }}<span class="unit">h</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="inspection-item">
            <div class="label">防水等级</div>
            <div class="value">{{ report.inspection.waterResistance ?: '—' }}</div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size:12px;color:#6b7280;">备注：{{ report.inspection.notes ?: '—' }}</p>
    {% else %}
    <p style="color:#9ca3af;font-size:12px;">暂无检测数据</p>
    {% endif %}

    <div class="section-title">🔧 维修与保养内容</div>
    <table>
        <thead>
        <tr>
            <th style="width:90px;">类型</th>
            <th>项目名称</th>
            <th style="width:80px;text-align:right;">数量</th>
            <th style="width:100px;text-align:right;">单价</th>
            <th style="width:100px;text-align:right;">小计</th>
        </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
        {% for item in report.serviceItems %}
        <tr>
            <td>{{ item.type == 'labor' ? '工时' : (item.type == 'part' ? '配件' : '其他') }}</td>
            <td>{{ item.name }}</td>
            <td style="text-align:right;">{{ item.quantity }}</td>
            <td style="text-align:right;">¥{{ '%.2f'|format(item.unitPrice) }}</td>
            <td style="text-align:right;font-weight:600;">¥{{ '%.2f'|format(item.subtotal) }}</td>
        </tr>
        {% endfor %}
        {% if report.serviceItems is empty %}
        <tr><td colspan="5" style="text-align:center;color:#9ca3af;padding:16px;">暂无收费项</td></tr>
        {% endif %}
        </tbody>
    </table>

    {% if report.partUsages is not empty %}
    <div class="section-title">📦 配件更换清单</div>
    <table>
        <thead>
        <tr>
            <th>配件名称</th>
            <th style="width:110px;">SKU</th>
            <th style="width:100px;">批号</th>
            <th style="width:60px;text-align:right;">数量</th>
            <th style="width:100px;text-align:right;">小计</th>
        </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
        {% for pu in report.partUsages %}
        <tr>
            <td>{{ pu.name }}</td>
            <td style="font-family:monospace;font-size:11.5px;">{{ pu.sku ?: '—' }}</td>
            <td>{{ pu.batchNumber ?: '—' }}</td>
            <td style="text-align:right;">{{ pu.quantity }}</td>
            <td style="text-align:right;font-weight:600;">¥{{ '%.2f'|format(pu.subtotal) }}</td>
        </tr>
        {% endfor %}
        </tbody>
    </table>
    {% endif %}

    {% if report.images.before or report.images.after %}
    <div class="section-title">📷 维修对比图</div>
    <div class="compare-images">
        {% if report.images.before is not empty %}
        <div>
            <img src="{{ report.images.before[0].url }}" alt="维修前" onerror="this.style.visibility='hidden'">
            <div class="caption">维修前</div>
        </div>
        {% endif %}
        {% if report.images.during is not empty %}
        <div>
            <img src="{{ report.images.during[0].url }}" alt="维修中" onerror="this.style.visibility='hidden'">
            <div class="caption">维修中</div>
        </div>
        {% endif %}
        {% if report.images.after is not empty %}
        <div>
            <img src="{{ report.images.after[0].url }}" alt="维修后" onerror="this.style.visibility='hidden'">
            <div class="caption">维修后</div>
        </div>
        {% endif %}
    </div>
    {% endif %}

    <div class="section-title">📈 服务进度</div>
    <div class="progress-timeline">
        {% for item in report.progress|slice(0, 20) %}
        <div class="item">
            <span class="time">{{ item.time }}</span>
            <span class="action">{{ item.action }}</span>
            <span class="detail">{{ item.detail }}</span>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
        {% if report.progress is empty %}
        <div style="color:#9ca3af;text-align:center;padding:16px;">暂无进度记录</div>
        {% endif %}
    </div>

    <div class="pricing-card">
        <h3 style="margin:0 0 14px;color:#1e40af;">💰 费用结算</h3>
        <div class="pricing-row"><span>工时费用</span><span class="amount">¥{{ '%.2f'|format(report.pricing.labor) }}</span></div>
        <div class="pricing-row"><span>配件费用</span><span class="amount">¥{{ '%.2f'|format(report.pricing.parts) }}</span></div>
        <div class="pricing-row"><span>已收定金</span><span class="amount">− ¥{{ '%.2f'|format(report.pricing.deposit) }}</span></div>
        <div class="pricing-row total">
            <span>合计应付</span>
            <span class="amount">¥{{ '%.2f'|format(report.pricing.total) }}</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    {% if report.warranty %}
    <div class="warranty-card">
        <span class="warranty-badge">🛡️ 质保服务</span>
        <span style="font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:#065f46;">
            {{ report.warranty.months }}个月整机质保 · {{ report.warranty.startDate }} 至 {{ report.warranty.endDate }}
        </span>
    </div>
    {% endif %}

    <div class="signatures">
        <div class="signature-block">
            <div style="margin-bottom:30px;">客户签字确认</div>
            <div>日期：_________________</div>
        </div>
        <div class="signature-block">
            <div style="margin-bottom:30px;">工程师签字 / 技术负责人</div>
            <div>日期：_________________</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-note">
        本报告一式两份，客户与工作室各执一份，具有同等效力。<br>
        如对服务质量有任何疑问，请于交付之日起15日内联系我们。 | {{ studio_name }}
    </div>
</body>
</html>
